Your privacy is important to us. This app does not collect any personal data and does not upload your practice records to the developer’s servers. You may choose to use the cloud synchronization service provided by your operating system to sync data across your devices. The synchronization process is provided and performed by the system platform and is used only for device-to-device synchronization. All data always belongs solely to you.
This app includes in-app purchases. All payments and order processing are provided and handled by the app distribution platform. The developer does not obtain your payment information or billing information. Data related to purchases is processed by the platform in accordance with its respective privacy policies. This app only receives the information necessary to confirm the purchase status in order to unlock the corresponding features.
